# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# S.A.M Framework — this repo contains ONLY S.A.M's own code, schemas, GUI and
# docs. Barony's source is a sibling folder outside this repo and is never
# tracked here (it belongs to Turning Wheel LLC). The entries below keep build
# artifacts, dependencies, and any stray copy of the game/engine out of commits.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# --- Node / React (gui/) ---
node_modules/
dist/
.vite/
*.local
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

# --- C++ build artifacts (framework is built into Barony elsewhere) ---
build/
out/
*.obj
*.o
*.exe
*.dll
*.lib
*.a
*.pdb
*.ilk
*.exp
*.idb

# --- Visual Studio / IDE ---
.vs/
*.user
*.suo
*.sln.docstates
*.vcxproj.user
CMakeCache.txt
CMakeFiles/
.idea/

# --- Barony / engine source — do NOT commit TurningWheel's code ---
# (defensive: these are siblings outside this repo, but guard anyway)
Barony/
barony-src/
baronymoreclasses/
sam_log.txt
log.txt
# NOTE: S.A.M's OWN bundled models under model-library/ are content and SHOULD
# be committed, so .vox/.png are intentionally NOT ignored here.

# --- OS cruft ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
